[SPEAKER_05]: It doesn't weigh in on what doctors can or can't do.

331
00:36:45,549 --> 00:36:49,531
[SPEAKER_05]: It doesn't make any statements or opinions about the industry of health care.

332
00:36:49,591 --> 00:36:50,832
[SPEAKER_05]: What it says is that

333
00:36:51,273 --> 00:37:06,243
[SPEAKER_05]: if somebody from another state is seeking to prosecute who's receiving healthcare or somebody who's administering healthcare that they're legally allowed to do in Massachusetts, then that patient or that provider cannot be prosecuted for seeking healthcare to which they're entitled.

334
00:37:06,263 --> 00:37:08,004
[SPEAKER_05]: So I'm really glad you asked for that clarification.

335
00:37:08,084 --> 00:37:08,464
[SPEAKER_05]: Thank you.

336
00:37:08,925 --> 00:37:10,766
