340
00:37:27,976 --> 00:37:30,537
[SPEAKER_02]: Are you fine with that?

341
00:37:33,457 --> 00:37:40,542
[SPEAKER_05]: Well, actually, Bill, I'm glad that you're sort of probing for these clarifications, because again, this is completely outside this ordinance.

342
00:37:40,582 --> 00:37:43,684
[SPEAKER_05]: What it doesn't do is weigh in on medical procedures whatsoever.

343
00:37:44,124 --> 00:37:49,608
[SPEAKER_05]: What it does is protect the jurisdiction of municipal Medford public safety resources.

344
00:37:50,929 --> 00:37:51,529
[SPEAKER_05]: Thank you so much.

345
00:37:51,569 --> 00:37:55,112
[SPEAKER_05]: Any additional comments from Zoom or in the chambers?

